OL,3,CKing Charles holds adapted state
OL,4,Cbanquet for Nigerian president
OL,6,FA state banquet has been adapted to
OL,7,Frespect the first state visit by a
OL,8,FMuslim head of state observing Ramadan
OL,9,Fin nearly a century.
OL,11,FThe King welcomed the Nigerian
OL,12,FPresident Bola Ahmed Tinubu and First
OL,13,FLady Oluremi Tinubu to St George's
OL,14,FHall in Windsor Castle for tonight's
OL,15,Fglittering state banquet.
OL,17,FMr Tinubu's stay is the first incoming
OL,18,Fstate visit by a Muslim leader during
OL,19,FRamadan since 1928 when King George V
OL,20,Fhosted King Amanullah Khan of
OL,21,FAfghanistan.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
