CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1773907468
OL,3,CKing Charles holds adapted state
OL,4,Cbanquet for Nigerian president
OL,6,FThe President broke his fast privately
OL,7,Fat sunset before joining the Royal
OL,8,FFamily for the banquet.
OL,10,FThe First Lady is a Christian and an
OL,11,Fordained Pentecostal pastor.
OL,13,FFor the first time in living memory,
OL,14,Fcanapes were offered ahead of the
OL,15,Fdinner to offer sustenance to Muslim
OL,16,Fguests who were unable to partake in
OL,17,Fiftar ` the breaking of their fast.
OL,19,FA prayer room has also been set up in
OL,20,Fthe castle for guests to use.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
