OL,3,CKing Charles holds adapted state
OL,4,Cbanquet for Nigerian president
OL,6,FThe Crimson Bloom has been inspired by
OL,7,Fthe classic Nigerian Chapman Cocktail,
OL,8,Fwhich is usually made with Fanta,
OL,9,FSprite and Angostura Bitters.
OL,11,FThe alcohol-free version for tonight's
OL,12,Fbanquet is made with homemade hibiscus
OL,13,Fand ginger syrup, sharpened with fresh
OL,14,Flemon and a hint of spice, and
OL,15,Flengthened with English Rose soda.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
