OL,3,CKing Charles holds adapted state
OL,4,Cbanquet for Nigerian president
OL,6,FThe 47-metre table has been adorned
OL,7,Fwith seasonal flowers and foliage from
OL,8,Fthe gardens of Buckingham Palace,
OL,9,FWindsor Castle and The Savill Gardens
OL,10,Fin Windsor Great Park.
